For those asking my for part 3...It's already out. Actually was released back in 2014. But is not a continuation...it's the same girl but now she just goes around fucking every bald old man she mets on the streets because they remind her of her uncle. Personally I find it disgusting and hate that kind of stuff but if you are into it give it a go. 

I won't post any link since I don't even feel like looking for it again. But it's called "Trip Out"
